 * <div id="function.ldap-get-dn" class="refentry"> <div class="refnamediv">  <h1 class="refname">ldap_get_dn</h1>  <p class="verinfo">(PHP 4, PHP 5, PHP 7, PHP 8)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">ldap_get_dn</span> — <span class="dc-title">Get the DN of a result entry</span></p> </div>  <div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-function.ldap-get-dn-description">  <h3 class="title">说明</h3>  <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description">   <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>ldap_get_dn</strong></span>(<span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.ldap-connection.php" class="type LDAP\Connection" style="color:#EAB766">LDAP\Connection</a></span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">\$ldap</span></span>, <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">LDAP\ResultEntry</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">\$entry</span></span>): <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.string.php" class="type string" style="color:#EAB766">string</a></span>|<span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.singleton.php" class="type false" style="color:#EAB766">false</a></span></span></div>  <p class="para rdfs-comment">   Finds out the DN of an entry in the result.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.ldap-get-dn-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><dl>         <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">ldap</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       通过 <span class="function">{@link ldap_connect()}</span> 返回的 <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.ldap-connection.php" class="classname">LDAP\Connection</a></span> 实例。      </p>     </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">entry</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.ldap-result-entry.php" class="classname">LDAP\ResultEntry</a></span> 实例。      </p>     </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.ldap-get-dn-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   Returns the DN of the result entry and <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.false">false</a></span></strong> on error.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 changelog" id="refsect1-function.ldap-get-dn-changelog">  <h3 class="title">更新日志</h3>  <table class="doctable informaltable">       <thead>     <tr>      <th>版本</th>      <th>说明</th>     </tr>    </thead>    <tbody class="tbody">     <tr> <td>8.1.0</td> <td>  现在 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">ldap</span> 参数接受 <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.ldap-connection.php" class="classname">LDAP\Connection</a></span>  实例，之前接受有效的 <span class="literal">ldap link</span> <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span>。 </td></tr>     <tr> <td>8.1.0</td> <td>  The <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">entry</span> parameter expects an <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.ldap-result-entry.php" class="classname">LDAP\ResultEntry</a></span>  instance now; previously, a valid <span class="literal">ldap result entry</span> <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span> was expected. </td></tr>    </tbody>     </table> </div></div>
