td>8.0.0</td><td>  <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">controls</span> is nullable now; previously, it defaulted to <span class="literal">[]</span>.</td></tr>      <tr>       <td>7.3.0</td>       <td>        Support for <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">controls</span> added       </td>      </tr>     </tbody>       </table>   </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.ldap-delete-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link ldap_delete_ext()} - Delete an entry from a directory</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link ldap_add()} - Add entries to LDAP directory</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
