.singleton.php" class="type false" style="color:#EAB766">false</a></span></span></div>  <p class="para rdfs-comment">   Does the same thing as <span class="function">{@link ldap_delete()}</span> but returns   an <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.ldap-result.php" class="classname">LDAP\Result</a></span> instance to be parsed with <span class="function">{@link ldap_parse_result()}</span>.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.ldap-delete-ext-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">    See <span class="function">{@link ldap_delete()}</span>  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.ldap-delete-ext-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   Returns an <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.ldap-result.php" class="classname">LDAP\Result</a></span> instance, 或者在失败时返回 <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.false">false</a></span></strong>.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 changelog" id="refsect1-function.ldap-delete-ext-changelog">  <h3 class="title">更新日志</h3>  <table class="doctable informaltable">       <thead>     <tr>      <th>版本</th>      <th>说明</th>     </tr>    </thead>    <tbody class="tbody">     <tr> <td>8.1.0</td> <td>  现在 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">ldap</span> 参数接受 <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.ldap-connection.php" class="classname">LDAP\Connection</a></span>  实例，之前接受有效的 <span class="literal">ldap link</span> <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span>。 </td></tr>     <tr> <td>8.1.0</td> <td>  Returns an <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.ldap-result.php" class="classname">LDAP\Result</a></span> instance now;  previously, a <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span> was returned. </td></tr>     <tr><td>8.0.0</td><td>  <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">controls</span> is nullable now; previously, it defaulted to <span class="literal">[]</span>.</td></tr>    </tbody>     </table> </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.ldap-delete-ext-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link ldap_delete()} - Delete an entry from a directory</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link ldap_parse_result()} - Extract information from result</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
