tants.php#constant.null">null</a></span></strong></span></span><br>): <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.boolean.php" class="type bool" style="color:#EAB766">bool</a></span></div>  <p class="para rdfs-comment">   Removes one or more attribute values from the specified <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">dn</span>.   Object deletions are done by the   <span class="function">{@link ldap_delete()}</span> function.  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-function.ldap-mod-del-parameters">  <h3 class="title">参数</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><dl>         <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">ldap</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       通过 <span class="function">{@link ldap_connect()}</span> 返回的 <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.ldap-connection.php" class="classname">LDAP\Connection</a></span> 实例。      </p>     </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">dn</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       The distinguished name of an LDAP entity.      </p>     </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">entry</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">      </p>     </dd>             <dt><span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">controls</span></dt>     <dd>      <p class="para">       Array of <a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/ldap.controls.php" class="link">LDAP Controls</a> to send with the request.      </p>     </dd>       </dl>   </div> <div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-function.ldap-mod-del-returnvalues">  <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>  <p class="para">   成功时返回 <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.true">true</a></span></strong>， 或者在失败时返回 <strong><span><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/reserved.constants.php#constant.false">false</a></span></strong>。  </p> </div> <div class="refsect1 changelog" id="refsect1-function.ldap-mod-del-changelog">  <h3 class="title">更新日志</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><table class="doctable informaltable">         <thead>      <tr>       <th>版本</th>       <th>说明</th>      </tr>     </thead>     <tbody class="tbody">      <tr> <td>8.1.0</td> <td>  现在 <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">ldap</span> 参数接受 <span class="classname"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/class.ldap-connection.php" class="classname">LDAP\Connection</a></span>  实例，之前接受有效的 <span class="literal">ldap link</span> <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766"><a href="https://php.net/manual/zh/language.types.resource.php" class="type resource" style="color:#EAB766">resource</a></span>。 </td></tr>      <tr><td>8.0.0</td><td>  <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">controls</span> is nullable now; previously, it defaulted to <span class="literal">[]</span>.</td></tr>      <tr>       <td>7.3.0</td>       <td>        Support for <span class="parameter" style="color:#3A95FF">controls</span> added       </td>      </tr>     </tbody>       </table>   </div> <div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-function.ldap-mod-del-seealso">  <h3 class="title">参见</h3>  <p class="para">   </p><ul class="simplelist">    <li><span class="function">{@link ldap_mod_del_ext()} - Delete attribute values from current attributes</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link ldap_mod_add()} - Add attribute values to current attributes</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link ldap_mod_replace()} - Replace attribute values with new ones</span></li>    <li><span class="function">{@link ldap_modify_batch()} - Batch and execute modifications on an LDAP entry</span></li>   </ul>   </div></div>
